= SDL_ClearError =

Clear any previous error message for this thread.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void SDL_ClearError(void);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 3.0.0.

== Code Examples ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c++'>
const char *error = SDL_GetError();
if (*error) {
  SDL_Log("SDL error: %s", error);
  SDL_ClearError();
}
</syntaxhighlight>

